{
  "stem": "7337.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And war broke out in 1914.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My father wouldn't have a child during the war, and hence, I was born in 1919, being a-- a year after the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First World War, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, up to a point.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The press was not-- I mean, the media in those days was not like it is today.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no television.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only radio communication with Germany was Hitler-- Hitler's broadcasts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But you-- you got far more hearsay that-- how things were particularly deteriorating from-- you know, as time went on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It got worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But basically, the Jews had a relatively [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] peaceful time from '33 to '37.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The real hell started in-- in 1937 until 19-- until the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, only by inference.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we couldn't reach them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- nobody knew where they were, so obviously, they had been taken away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we be applied to the South African legation, and Eric Louw, who was probably South Africa's most anti-Semitic [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] minister, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was the most charming, helpful minister plenipotentiary in France.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he was unbelievably helpful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] He said my father must come and open a hat factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We want secondary industry in South Africa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We need people with money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he really made every effort to-- to get all the formalities of our immigration [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] sorted out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father told him, he says, well, that's fine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But if I start a factory, then I have to bring a foreman out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was born in Chelmno.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Louw said, well, where's Chelmno?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, Chelmno's in Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
